snippet.title: Pocket Puyo Puyo 2/Tsu (1996, Gameboy) - 1 of 5: Story Mode (Hardest)[720p60]
snippet.description:
This is much more faster (compared to Pocket Puyo Puyo) and much more like it.

although it's hard to tell which garbage puyo are the normal garbage puyo or the points puyo
————————————————————————————
Played on Hardest difficulty.

The video contains static in the sound, this is caused by Fraps and VisualBoyAdvance not wanting to cooperate. Nothing I can do about that.

Floor 01 - 00:41 (Skeleton T, Nomi)
Floor 02 - 04:04 (Mummy)
Floor 03 - 05:55 (Harpy, Samurai Mole)
Floor 04 - 07:52 (Watch, Hamono)
Floor 05 - 06:43 (Draco)
Schezo - 13:03
Rulue - 13:49
Satan - 14:59

Ending - 16:03
